Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found the melody of Aquarion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect melody I've been searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade, you know your body—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.34,0:00:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to play that melody with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the fiery depths of Hell take my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a special permission waiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this quest of yours can only end with death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only hear the melody of life because death comes with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you satisfied, my classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It has been one full week since the Berlin fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yet we men and women are still separated by unseen walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We must tear down the walls between us and share ourselves with one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno, he just got up there and started making some dumb speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, I think that's enough—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My classmates, I motion for an emergency seating change!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this just to switch seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing seats is out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If men and women mix any further, \Nthe taint will be impossible to cleanse!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I second the motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be fun! I call next to Cayenne!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all impure! Unclean! Tainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how do we pick seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can draw for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw for Cayenne and Shrade, since they're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all sunshine and holes... I mean roses for me from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Malloy. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the mock battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Ei Chan. It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the people to sit next to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those big bangs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Amata!{yoroshiku}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi.{returning yoroshiku}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!{yoroshiku}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's going to get hot around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't mean out in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cayenne and Shrade are sitting next to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be God's gift to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, I just can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time we've sat by each other, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the last if I can help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming for me, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was investigating the Abductors, and while I was here—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eyes on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Your sound is clumsy and depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was making a joke, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, why does everyone look so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who just left this cat doll here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doll, huh? I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaaaah! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doll of dread, right here with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about an Element who disappeared in Neo-Deava.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened a few years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl transferred into the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was timid and shy, and couldn't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, she couldn't stand to be alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one day, she vanished from the Academy.{holy shit it makes sense now}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have been so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl had just one friend, her doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doll appears at night, wandering around campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you can hear its sad, lonely voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,singing of the girl's tragedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually heard that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the Berlin fell, that doll has \Neven been spotted in the boys' dorms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malloy believes it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doll just moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you cut the crap already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it! It actually moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know the simulation is to prepare you for real combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, he's not getting out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An invisible door, a door to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly to the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna check what's on the other side of the door again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last son of Altair...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, uh... Zessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evening! Cleaning duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What a coincidence! I'm going back to my dorm too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy! I'm accompanying you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! It's locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we have to sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in opposite ways now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come in from the girls' side?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, okay, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't walk if you're doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared of moving dolls or singing ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not even real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just some stupid story!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is someone's idea of a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stink deliciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared... but that wasn't all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't stop thinking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop grabbing me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... not Zessica and Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here, Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your hands off my smelly wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you can lead us to our true Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, the cat doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! In the hall, in the middle of the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, you saw it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, it was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you taking it seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was your story in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was even walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we heard it singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at the age where you start seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same age as us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a more important question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you two doing together so late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that? Zessica was—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell them I was scared! You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two whispering to each other about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I, we, it—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you sullied our holy Academy's grounds by—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw the walking doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I saw Zessica and Amata running \Nacross the courtyard in each other's arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Zessica was screaming at Amata, "Don't leave me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they were having a lovers' spat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong! Come on, Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Abductors detected in the Neo-Kowloon area!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}All Elements report to phase one battle stations immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Repeat, all Elements report to phase one battle stations immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Analysis complete. Pattern B.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceeding just like in the simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Abductor has taken down all of the wall structures!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving at 60 kph!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange. It's not trying to capture anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let it do any more damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica, you're the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're with Cayenne and Amata. Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono's really mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know the range or accuracy of the enemy's laser fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being ambushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its aiming error is 0.0003%.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! He can aim a laser through atmosphere that precisely?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Radius Gnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can spot a coin from a thousand villages away,{literal of 千里, it means a ridiculously long distance but just saying that isn't poetic enough}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fire an unerring arrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,strike true, and pierce straight through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Union now! A Vector wouldn't survive one hit from that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly low and close in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Union! Go, Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Gepard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That area has already been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're allowed to use the buildings for cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still out of range of our attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stay in cover and close the distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can read your movements like a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just overwhelm you and pin you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is releasing small flying objects!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Now we're screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those floating objects are reflecting the lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's lasers can attack from all directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can no longer use their surroundings as cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're up against a whole army!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Z is taking the brunt of the laser fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata Sora's spirit level is falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hit the limit! The Union is breaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good enough at controlling Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica's spirit level is falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's below 40, now 30%!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Amata's the one taking damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peoples' hearts cannot be seen with the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so they misunderstand one another and drive each other apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:17:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Mikono Suzushiro, there is a purpose for things unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we shall find strength in those hearts that we cannot see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Element Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch out Zessica Wong for Yunoha Thrul!{think it's a joke on "through"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, Zessica, I'm really sorry for surprising you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sorry that Mikono made a mistake because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you saw something like that late at night, you'd freak out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please, you have to trust me and let me fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an Element?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we do this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, will you still... Union with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spectral Union! Go, Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! They'll see me! They'll all see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see her! I can really see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you really look like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want them to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it feels nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Evol!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Machine Angel's other form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was in the simulation too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the student who disappeared! She rematerialized!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop looking at me! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lasers went right through us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her shyness expands to cover her, making her transparent to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yunoha Thrul's Element power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what the soul of a beautifully shy young lady can accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. I can't keep all of Aquarion transparent for very long at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Works for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, if you compliment me like that, I'll get shy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My lasers don't hit, and it's vanished from all my sensors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't in the simulation at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're only 800m from the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep closing in on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just invisible to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see you, but you're still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can still shoot you with solid bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it gone yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting overwhelmed! Pinned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit him with a fist he can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subliminal Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the ghost do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's the best I can do with this transdimensional remote control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, I got data on a new Rare Igura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invisibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I jumped to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the new member of our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. My name is Yunoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ghost of that dead Element, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:21:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm not scared of you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Amata?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha Thrul is an Element student, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh god! Let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll fly for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.09,0:24:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Zessica Wong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.12,0:24:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty famous for a 17 year old,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.56,0:24:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they say I expose way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.25,0:24:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the depths of my cleavage may be open for all to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but not a soul knows the depths of my heart. {but the depths of my heart are a se~cr~et~}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.53,0:24:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next time on Aquarion Evol: Revelations.
