Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.01,0:01:15.77,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Even if you're scared
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.50,0:01:20.33,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Just live your life, don't give up now, keep moving on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.47,0:01:25.65,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}And I'll come for you over and over and over again
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.04,0:01:31.24,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}We'll find each other soon enough
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.91,0:01:37.48,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}By the faintest glimmer of starlight
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.66,0:01:43.50,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}I know you, I know you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.92,0:01:52.69,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}It's been billions of years, but now we can open the door to our legend
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.71,0:01:58.17,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}I crossed over the deep blue void
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.60,0:02:03.57,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}so I could burn to ash along with you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.44,0:02:16.29,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}I've had a long journey on the vast wheel of fate, gathering sorrows along the way
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.31,0:02:21.94,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}I'm not perfect, but I'm giving all I have
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.25,0:02:27.80,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}If I open my fragile heart to you, I know I'll bleed...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.13,0:02:33.80,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}But I'll always be with you, always be in your arms
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.80,0:02:38.28,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}We'll get on a shining ship of light
