Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:48.97,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}kaze ni ubawareta wake janai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:48.97,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}We weren't spirited away on the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:53.25,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}katamichi bun no yuuki de bokura
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:53.25,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}We knew we could never return, and found the courage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:59.30,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}higeki wo ukeireru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:59.30,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}to accept the hardship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.18,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}kokoro ga koko ni atta hazu no kuudou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.18,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}There's an emptiness where my heart used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:07.19,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}motto boku ga ookikereba
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:07.19,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}If only I was stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:12.82,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}kimi wo mirai wo sukueta darou ka
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:12.82,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}I could have saved you, and our future...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:20.19,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}taisetsu na hito wo mamoru sube ga tatta hitotsu shika motanai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:20.19,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}I only know of one way to keep the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:26.48,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}sonna anata ga haguretadayou sora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:26.48,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}And you left me and disappeared into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:34.23,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}anata ijou no hito ni deaenai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:34.23,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}I'll never find anyone like you again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:40.58,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}tsuki ni aragau nagai furea
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:40.58,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}A long flare reaches out against the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:47.38,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}hajimaru mo sezu owaru monogatari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:47.38,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}The story ends before it could even begin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:51.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}kizutsukiuru yawarakasa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:51.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}So soft, so fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:54.81,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}tojikometa senritsu kanaderu hodo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:54.81,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}I will call up the melody locked away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.14,0:24:00.82,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}utau hodo kowareru hodo ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.14,0:24:00.82,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}And sing it until I destroy myself
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:08.63,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\fad(0,300)}anata ga koishii
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:08.63,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}That's how much I love you
